content.rendered:
BOSS AIR OUTBACK AIR PRO 3

Boss Air Outback Air Pro 3 available for order now through Automax 4×4! Order online, come in & see us or give us a call on (02) 6699 2744 for a quote!

This kit is suitable to run air lockers, inflate tires, run small air tools and situations where bigger volume air is needed but space is tight.

Includes:

  • 1 x PX-07 3/4 hp 12 volt BOSS Air Compressor
  • 1 x AT-03 3 Gallon/ 9ltr Boss Aluminium Air Tank
  • 1 x 110-135psi Pressure Switch
  • 1 x 700mm Teflon Coated Stainless Steel Braided Hose
  • 1 x 100% Duty Solenoid
  • 1 x Check Valve
  • 1 x Flare Fitting
  • 1 x Drain Tap
  • 1 x 1/4”NPT Bung
  • Instruction Sheet

Extra Options Available;

  • Remote Nitto Add-on
    • Add a remote Nitto Coupling so you can “plug-in” to pump up tyres or use air tools

To view the range of Boss Air products available, CLICK HERE!

Follow us on Instagram and Facebook to keep up to date with what’s going on in our workshop!
